Flash Briefing Skill
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
des:
Alexa reads the headlines form today's "The UAV Daily news paper. To read the full stories, please visit www.TheUAVDaily.com.

The UAV Daily news provides daily news articles about Drones (Unmanned Aerial Vehicles), RC aircraft, and other related aviation and robotics stories.

The UAV Daily, and this Alexa skill, are brought to you by Mike Flys from www.MikeFlys.com
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
